(5, 'Admission Test Result of MBA Program', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><strong>Stamford University Bangladesh</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><strong>Summer 2019 Trimester</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><strong>Admission Test Result of MBA Program</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">Students bearing the following roll numbers have been qualified for admission in the MBA program on the basis of written test (held on&nbsp;<strong>March 29, 2019</strong>) and viva voce (held on&nbsp;<strong>March 31, 2019</strong>):</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><strong>00003, 00005, 00007, 00008, 00010, 00011, 00012, 05001, 05004, 05005, 05006, 05007, 05008, 05009, 05010, 05011, 05012, 05013, 05014, 05015, 05016, 05018, 05020, 05023, 05031, 05032, 05033, 05035, 05037</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">They are advised to complete admission formalities by&nbsp;<strong>April 09, 2019</strong><strong>:</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><strong>Admission requirements are:</strong></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none;\"><strong>Initial Payment :</strong>&nbsp;<strong>27,400/=</strong></li></ul><ol style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-st